            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Focused learning experience for better retention</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Reduced homework pressure on young minds</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Better subject understanding through deep immersion</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> More time for hands-on activities and practical learning</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Age-appropriate teaching methods for LKG to 4th Class</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Balanced curriculum covering all essential subjects</li>
